      <p style="padding: 5px 0;">Welcome to the Common Threads family of monthly
        supporters - our Action Collective! We are grateful that you have chosen
        to join our mission. As you know, we are a small organization trying to
        meet massive needs, so with your ongoing contributions you enable and
        empower us in our work.</p>

      <p style="padding: 5px 0;">Together we’re making transformative trauma
        healing accessible to more survivors of gender-based violence, war, and
        conflict. With a monthly gift of
        {{donationAmount}}, beginning on
        {{donationStartDate}}, you are providing a lifeline for survivors of
        sexual violence around the world.
      </p>

      <p style="padding: 5px 0;">As a monthly donor, you have joined a special
        club of supporters who are sustaining the recovery process for the women
        and girls in our programs. By becoming part of the CTP Action
        Collection, you are giving not only material resources but also belief
        in the work of healing, and this produces a sense of hope. All of us in
        the Common Threads Family are very grateful that you have made this
        commitment. Your monthly gift means that you are sponsoring a survivor
        for the long-term healing and resilience she deserves.</p>

